Home.

48:01.003 --> 48:04.041
Amanda?

48:04.340 --> 48:06.673
Come.

48:09.261 --> 48:12.095
Oh.
Hungry.

48:24.110 --> 48:26.727
You did it.
We did it.

48:30.366 --> 48:32.858
Um... excuse me.

48:37.748 --> 48:39.614
Those two trees
