with big white pillars in front.

53:07.017 --> 53:08.849
What brought you to the clinic?

53:09.144 --> 53:12.808
A sergeant in my outfit
in the army named Cal Edwards.

53:13.107 --> 53:14.939
He was from Washington Street.

53:17.027 --> 53:19.565
- You don't want to hear about it, do you?
- Cal Edwards.

53:19.863 --> 53:21.946
He's not one
of our patients, is he?

53:22.241 --> 53:24.858
He was killed on the other
side of the world.

53:25.160 --> 53:27.447
Where's the ice cream stand?

53:27.746 --> 53:30.454
He must have been
a very good friend of yours.

53:30.749 --> 53:33.207
He saved my life once.

53:33.502 --> 53:38.293
So I figured I owed him and Washington Street
a few of the years he gave me.

53:38.590 --> 53:40.923
Anyway, I learned more here
than I would in the suburbs...

53:41.218 --> 53:43.961
giving out diet pills
and vitamin shots.

53:48.559 --> 53:50.596
Say it, Amanda.
Go on, say it.

53:50.894 --> 53:53.056
Ice cream, ice cream, ice cream.

53:53.355 --> 53:56.189
Good girl.
Let's get some.

54:02.614 --> 54:05.527
Up we go, baby.
That's a girl.

54:05.826 --> 54:08.864
Amanda wants strawberry.
Make that two.

54:10.038 --> 54:12.872
And for the missus?
Uh...

54:14.710 --> 54:17.748
chocolate.
Here you go, kiddo.

54:18.046 --> 54:20.129
